  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following tasks provide information on the development of project-specific method assets.&amp;nbsp; They are performed&#xD;
    in conjunction with the method development steps of this task:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        See &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot; href=&quot;./../../core.base_rup/tasks/prepare_project_specific_guidelines_A9AD00DB.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;{1E706674-C1E7-4F8D-BF06-35FFE49C5E42}&quot;>Task: Prepare Guidelines for the Project&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;for guidance on&#xD;
        harvesting and tailoring of project-specific guidelines.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        See &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot; href=&quot;./../../core.base_rup/tasks/prepare_project_specific_templates_F4BB56.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;{456ACFD8-B1F7-4B18-ABBE-D58D88C9E7C6}&quot;>Task: Prepare Templates for the Project&lt;/a> for guidance on&#xD;
        harvesting and tailoring of project-specific templates.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
  <keyConsiderations>&lt;p>&#xD;
    An &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../core.base_rup/workproducts/rup_development_organization_assessment_A0186DDE.html&quot;&#xD;
    guid=&quot;{FA77EBA9-75C7-4AA2-934A-B88BED853CBE}&quot;>assessment of the development organization&lt;/a>, if available, indicates&#xD;
    which areas the development organization as a whole needs to focus on. An informed decision on which of the identified&#xD;
    improvement areas should be targeted for the project needs to be made. This decision directly affects the scope of the&#xD;
    tailoring effort&lt;i>.&lt;/i>&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Tailoring the process for a project should be treated as a project in its own right, with separate plans, budget and&#xD;
    control mechanisms. You should define a business case for it, based on return-on-investment analysis. The actual&#xD;
    development of the plug-in will benefit from following the lifecycle and disciplines in the RUP. We recommend that you&#xD;
    try out the main ideas behind the plug-in on a real project before you start the project to develop the plug-in.&#xD;
&lt;/p></keyConsiderations>
